name: Aurum Elf
skill: Reduces a random enemy (melee priority)'s DEF by 1436/1716 for a limited time.
ability: Moderately increases all Divina team members' Crit Rate when Platina Elf is on the team.

additional_data.description: The spirit of an elf based on one of the periodic elements. She rarely appears front and center in any of their songs, but many fans love her nonetheless. Some secretly hope that she might someday outshine the likes of Titanium and Platina. But she has no desire to be the star of the show. She just wants to enjoy music as much as she can, whether that's in a live show or offstage.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Limited Jewel Summon 03/05/17 to 10/05/17
◦ Trade at Exchange for 200 Mochi 03/05/17 - 10/05/17
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Summon rate increased until 10/05/17
◦ Can only be exchanged once 
° She was formerly nicknamed "Alumina" in "Spirit Idol Competition" event.

summon: "I love it when we put on a good show together."
limit_break: "Sometimes I have my chance to shine, too."
